titleInfo.title: Precision Industries, Inc. v. Tyson Foods, Inc.
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER - The plaintiff's motion to compel 42 is granted. Tyson Foods, Inc. shall supplement its responses for Interrogatories Nos. 4 and 5 on or before May 7, 2010. ADMONITION Pursuant to NECivR 72.2 any appeal of this Order shall be filed with the Clerk of the Court within fourteen (14) days after being served with a copy of this Order. Failure to timely appeal may constitute a waiver of any objection to the Order. The brief in support of any appeal shall be filed at the time of filing such appeal. Failure to file a brief in support of any appeal may be deemed an abandonment of the appeal. Ordered by Magistrate Judge Thomas D. Thalken. (KBJ)
